Definition: in a curt, abrupt and discourteous manner
Example: he told me curtly to get on with it; he talked short with everyone; he said shortly that he didn't like it
Synonyms: adj, all, discourteous, curt, short, shortly, in, a, abrupt, and, manner, he, told, me, to, get, on, with, it, talked, everyone, said, that, didn, t, like
Category: adv.all
